metadata.name: quarantine games
metadata.description: Life suddenly changed for everyone and in order to keep the mind and body in line with predictive programming as the elite needs and in a state associated with an unreal atmosphere, we placed ourselves in a dimension parallel to this with the pinball that could channel the situation and allow us to evade this cruel reality and whoever achieves the highest score to avoid getting infected and thus fall into quarantine or finally escape from an imminent fatal mutation.
